# This is a much longer run that I've included as a longer recorded reference. This assumes a new game, but starting with enough money to buy all the movement abilities in the game from the outset (I normally use 1e100, and so I'm calling it golden-spoon% :P). It's just a recording with no tweaks of running through the game, buying all abilities and finishing the demo - great for testing desyncs in longer runs and an easy setup

